<L>__{ext derelict buildings dawn}
<A>__{the wagon stands, hidden, among deserted derelict buildings. all is quiet. the lid of the big travelling trunk slowly opens. the man struggles out. his neck is sore, his wrists ache and his head is bruised. he hasn't a clue where he is. he tries to make sense of the wagon, the grazing horses, the derelict buildings. some distance away a bizarre, horned and tailed creature is involved in a strange contorted dance. hoping to avoid the creature, the man starts to move away but is stopped by a squeaky voice behind him.}
<C>__{percy }
<D>__{hey, you!}
<A>__{the man turns around to find percy looking at him.}
