<D>__{hanging?}
<C>__{percy}
<P>__{(handing parnassus the noose)}
<D>__{by his neck. until dead. if we'd had any sense.}
<A>__{anton produces the bricks with strange markings that were in the man's pockets.}
<C>__{anton}
<D>__{we found these in his p pockets.}
<A>__{doctor parnassus examines the bricks with great interest. he pulls out the hanged man card and compares it's arcane details a noose, strangely marked shapes like bricks, a metal tube to the objects found on the man.}
